net.anthavio.aspect
Class LogAspect

java.lang.Object
  net.anthavio.aspect.LogAspect

public class LogAspect
extends Object

AspectJ aspect logs execution of any method marked with Logged annotation. When class is annotated, all public method executions are logged. On INFO log level, only argument types (class) are logged (exception - null argument is logged every time) On DEBUG log level, argument and return values (toString()) are logged

vanek
